Co-authored-by: Chase Sterling <chase.sterling@gmail.com>
Widen plexapi version range, and move it to plugin dependencies

Try using poetry and caching more when running tests in github actions

Tweak imdb matching results to prefer earlier matches more.
Return movie directly if searched for imdb id or url
